title: Money & Economy - We were told to ignore it - Don't
description:
As a JW we were told to not worry about money and getting a good Job. 

Well seeing as we probably will get old, it is wise to at least understand how it works.

Some examples from people that used it well and an interesting look at economy.

Robert T Kiyosaki - Rich Dad, Poor Dad

Robert Kiyosaki   - Why A Students Work for C Students

Richard Branson   - Losing My Virginity 

Steven Levitt & Stephen Dubner - Freakonomics expanded
                              
                               - Superfreakonomics

Warren Buffett and the Business of Life by Alice Schroeder - The Snowball
